import React from 'react'

export default function AddPatient({handleAddSubmit, handleCancelBtn}) {
  return (
    <>
    <form className="form-group" onSubmit={handleAddSubmit}>
  <input className="form-control" type='text' name='first_name' placeholder='First Name' style={{ marginBottom: '10px' }} />
  <input className="form-control" type='text' name='last_name' placeholder='Last Name' style={{ marginBottom: '10px' }} />
  <input className="form-control" type='text' name='blood' placeholder='Blood Group' style={{ marginBottom: '10px' }} />

  <button className="btn btn-primary btn-sm" type='submit'>Submit</button>
  <button className="btn btn-secondary btn-sm" onClick={handleCancelBtn}>Cancel</button>
</form>

    </>
  )
}
